Description: Package manager for the Ethos language
 Forge installs and manages Traits for Ethos. Soft Traits are Python
 packages pulled from PyPI or local wheels, extracted into ~/.ethos/traits/.
 Hard Traits are compiled C/C++/Rust binaries loaded via ctypes. Forge
 never runs install scripts and works entirely from the standard library.
 Use alongside ethos-lang or standalone to manage your Ethos environment.
